Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should do this every day.\NThe sun will do you good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[wind howling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,FATHER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sidoh]\NHi, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidoh, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, quit following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, guess I shouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Things got a little complicated recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I not surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I told you,\Nstop following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give me back my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[exasperated]\NI don't know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it back, you're gonna have to\Nlook for it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron.\N[continues munching apple loudly]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Shuichi Aizawa] Wammy's House\Nisn't exactly a normal orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a school\Nfor gifted children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But here's the crazy part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Its real purpose is to groom these kids\Nso that one of them can become the next L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light Yagami] L's successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Apparently the one most likely\Nto succeed L
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is this kid named Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near. Is that N?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we founds some leads on Mello,\Nthe one N mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's smart too,\Nbut he always came second to Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] So Near was meant to be\NL's successor. There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to be N.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one commanding\Nthe SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Mello, he would have wanted\Nto become L's successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But he probably lost out to Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That gives him a motive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for wanting to get his hands on\Nthe notebook first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It all adds up perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is definitely the same Mello\Nthat N told us about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa]\NThese are sketches of both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't find any photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] L's successors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm still fighting L\Nafter all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But first thing's first.\NI have to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,where Mello and his mafia associates\Nare hiding themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I already had Misa check\Na list of known Mafia syndicates
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,using her Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa Amane gasps] Look, I found him.\NI can't see his lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's number 105.\NThey have him listed as Jack Neylon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But his real name is Kal Snydar.\NHe's got the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] After that, it was the simple\Nmatter of using the death note
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to make Snydar send a letter to me with\Nthe location of the gang's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be arriving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[door creaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Hi, Light.\NGreat news! The letter arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light]\NHe's in LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it. I out-maneuvered\Nboth Near and Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have the notebook\Nand Misa's eyes, I'm unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Light. I guess this means\NI was helpful to you again, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NI love you, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa sighs, giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sidoh]\NLos Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The next step is for me to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,just how much I can control people\Nwith this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sidoh] Oh, they're gonna have to\Nbe able to see me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,before I can even talk to them.\NWhat a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Snydar is\Nthe owner right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll have to make him\Ntouch the notebook first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sidoh] Tag, you're it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...\NThe notebook just flew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]\NIt's a notebook that kills people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell,\Nnothing surprises me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]\NBoss, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy in the freaky costume,\Nwho the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who brought him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here on my own.\NI'm actually a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] A Shinigami?\N[laughs hysterically]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want everyone to think\Nyou're crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,pass the notebook around\Nso they can see me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-[groans]\N-[notebook slides on floor]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He says you can see him\Nif you touch the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]\NPlease, everyone, touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'm not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Whatever.\NCome on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[bullet casings clink on floor]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try.\NYou humans can't kill a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack's right.\NThat ain't no costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a real, live Shinigami.\NSo now what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, I'm going to forfeit ownership\Nof this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All I ask is that you agree to follow\Nwhichever person I give it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] What?\NYou're giving up ownership again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] But wait. Won't you lose\Nall your memories if you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, lend me your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it on me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, even if I forfeit ownership\Nof my notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you as many pages you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to be Kira.\NCan you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. But I don't get\Nwhy you're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain everything to you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud munching]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chocolate is so good.\N-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that stuff you told us?\NIs it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"If the person using the note\Nfails to consecutively write
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,names of people to be killed\Nwithin 13 days of each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,then the user will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make this note unusable\Nby tearing it up or burning it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,all the humans who have touched\Nthe note till then will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying\Nthose two rules were made up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[clears throat]\NOh yeah, those rules are definitely fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is some Shinigami wrote those\Ndown as a joke
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,before giving the notebook\Nto a human. [munches]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] As for the 13-day rule, we can\Ntest that out by using one of our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the real question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was this the notebook\Nthat was used by Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, was he aware\Nthat these two rules were false?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If he did know, he could have used\Nthese rules to his advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the 13-day rule would have allowed him\Nto prove his innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in only 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[keeps munching]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Mello] Sidoh, go keep watch outside.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be very convenient for us\Nthat you can't be seen by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go outside and keep watch. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sidoh] What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's human,\Nbut he's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Touta Matsuda] What did he say?\N-[Soichiro Yagami] Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] I understand that the notebook\Nthat was in your possession
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,has fallen into criminal hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami]\NCan you prove that you are the real Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] Prove it? Now that there are others\Nusing the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point in predicting killings\Nin order to identify myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They could just as easily kill\Nthe same targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry,\NI've already taken this into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sent you something that will\Nclearly prove to you that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my own notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Wha... What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira]\NThe notebook I've sent you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,gives me the power to know\Na person's name by only seeing their face,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will be able to gain\Nthat same power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Please stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gathered information\Nfrom the FBI and other sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,On November 10th, at exactly 11:59 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,arrangements have been made\Nso that all known associates
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-of the mafia will die.\N-[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira/Misa]\NIt's already written in my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's impossible for me to make\Nany changes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not be able\Nto prevent these deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know their location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I will hand over that information\Nalong with the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,on November 10th, 11:59 p.m.,\Nthat's when it all happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment is your best\Nand only chance to get the notebook back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Mafia members are going to die\Non the day Kira specified,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be a chance to get\Nthe notebook back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the idea of following\NKira's plan, but it's our best option.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk]\NExactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing the time of death\Nfor these guys
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't going to be enough for us\Nto make our move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[stammers] Ide, I think we both know\Nwhat needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We get the Shinigami\Nto follow us in,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we do the deal for the eyes\Nand make sure they're all dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make the deal for the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[excitedly] No way, chief.\NLet me be the one to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was responsible for handing over\Nthe notebook in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that moment, I've been unable\Nto live with what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've even thought of killing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use the notebook\Nto kill any criminals who try to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And after 13 days, I'll die as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light]\NIf Dad writes a name in the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then...\Nwhen the time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,NOVEMBER 10, 23:47
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Report,\Nis everybody ready to move in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[all] Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Deputy Director,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,make the eye deal\Nwith the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Ryuk. I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[loud rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[high pitched noise rings out]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're finished,\NI want you to look at the photographs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the criminals I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see their names and life spans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami]\NYes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Their name should disappear soon.\NThat's your cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[clock ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, move in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] So, Kira's involved\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he'd go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My plan was supposed to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. What the hell is Sidoh doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, Sidoh.\NJust shut up and watch, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is sit here\Nand do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can do that,\Nyou'll get your notebook back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Roy. Skyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The notebook is under Rod's body
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it to\Nthe surveillance room upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa yells] Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] L, we've apprehended two\Nof the criminals .
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also been able to secure\Nthe notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa]\NWe'll being withdrawing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-[man] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] We still haven't found anyone\Nwho resembles our picture of Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That means he must be hiding\Nsomewhere in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this.\NDo a thorough search.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[men scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] What's was that?\N-[Aizawa] An explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already blown up the two entrances\Nto this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be your only warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The next explosion will take out\Nthe entire building
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as all your men inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you better do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light]\NIt's Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Mello chuckles]\N-[Yagami] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should have killed you\Nwhen I had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,History repeats itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never dreamed in a million years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd be bargaining for the notebook\Nwith you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[high pitched noise rings out]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami]\NM-I-H-A-E-L K-E-E-H-L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your real name is Mihael Keehl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello]\NWhat the hell...? How did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, Mello.\NIt's time to turn yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give up, I won't kill you.\NYou have my word on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light]\NWhat are you doing? Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Write his name down and kill him!\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how this works.\NI write your name and you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of that trigger\Nand put your hands in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Mello] Yagami...\N-Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've written your first name
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will only take me a second\Nto write your surname.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light grumbles]\NYou idiot! Just write it! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For what it's worth, I give you my word\Nthat I never wanted to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But tell me, Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never killed someone before,\Nhave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[bullet casings clink on floor]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[man]\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Jose! The notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Jose] Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy.\NHe won't let go of the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Son of a... [strains]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-[footsteps]\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Deputy Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa]\NIt's all over, Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands up and surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Matsuda, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] I'm sure you'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] L, I don't see any sign of Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[breathes uneasily]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Damn it. After all that,\Nhe got away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you should have\Njust killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[wind blowing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[monitor beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Come on, please, Dad.\NYou can't die on me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have them.\NI still have the Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,According to that Shinigami, Ryuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see the lifespan of someone\Nwho owns a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can see the numbers above your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You really aren't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.\NMy son...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me\Nyou're still worried about that, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he's not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you shouldn't talk so much, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's important, but I've got\Nbigger things to deal with right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get him\Nto write Mello's name in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I couldn't do it.\NI couldn't bring myself to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I can't just come out and say,\N"It's not too late."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No wait, maybe I can.\NIt all depends on how I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will think it's weird\Nif I get upset and panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad, write his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't let him beat you like this.\NWrite his name, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,With your last bit of strength!\NDo you want to die in vain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,D-- Dad, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami, softly] Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[monitor beeping goes flat]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling] Come on, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you die on me, you idiot!\NDad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Shinigami who came here\Nto take back this notebook, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sidoh] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] The notebook might be helpful\Nto the Kira investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but we really only need one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give this one back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sidoh] Humans who use the notebook\Nare cursed with fear, pain and misery. Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\NSoichiro didn't use the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He got to die believing\Nhis son wasn't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,he was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED